  "instructions_to_main_agent": [
    "Build this app using React Native EXPO (with React Native component styling).",
    "Apply the exact Brand Colors (Navy #1B2A4A, Red #C8102E, White #FFFFFF) heavily. Headers should strictly be Navy.",
    "Utilize victory-native for all charts, specifically leveraging custom color scales derived from the brand palette above.",
    "Implement the 16 screens using a nested Stack + Bottom Tab navigation architecture (5 bottom tabs).",
    "Ensure all touch targets (buttons, inputs) are at least 48px in height for mobile usability.",
    "Cards must have subtle shadows (`shadow-sm` equivalent in RN) against a light grey (`#F8F9FA`) background to achieve the 'clean white cards' luxury look.",
    "All interactive elements MUST include `testID` attribute (React Native equivalent of `data-testid`)."
  ]
}